fields.name: Agility - Illinois
fields.description:
Cone sprint agility test - 
Measures boxers' agility

Use a 10m x 5m rectangle.

Place 4 cones at the corners to mark the rectangle.

Place 4 cones down the center line, each spaced 3.3m apart.

Boxer goes around all cones as fast as possible.
